items.name: IamRoleBuster
items.description: This project is a Python-based tool designed to enumerate IAM roles in a specific AWS account, given the account ID. By leveraging AWS permissions, the script attempts to update the AssumeRole policy document of a provided or newly created role to discover existing roles within the target account.
